title: [Parts of Brant, Waterloo, and Wentworth Counties, 1951-05-14] : [A13118-Photo 174]
description: Stereoscopic coverage. Shows part of Brant County east of Brantford. Part of Waterloo County south of Kitchener, including Cambridge. Part of Wentworth County covering Puslinch, Carlisle, Killbride, Waterdown, Dundas Valley and the western half of the City of Hamilton. On verso: Royal Canadian Air Force, Crown copyright. Source: National Air Photo Library [Parts of Brant, Waterloo and Wentworth Counties] Operation VPH 252/51 Hamilton, May 14, 1951, September 9, 1951 and April 22, 1952.
